data.description: This 2224 square foot home is located in a quiet well-maintained neighborhood in the desirable Zia school district. This spacious home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2 car garage. You won't believe the quality of space provided with the eat-in kitchen, formal dining room, and TWO living spaces! This home is ready for lots of guests! Whether you're looking for a space to work on your hobbies or simply unwind with friends, the backyard man cave has got you covered. Don't miss out on seeing this unique home. Call Summer today 850-376-4659
